room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Gypsies" by Escape Room Studios in Detroit
room_description: A rogue gypsy couple, Boris and Doris, have concocted a new blend of Thieves Oil - and you want it. So you discover and sneak onto their caravan - a vintage Airstream coach and begin to search for your prize, which you must find and escape within 60 minutes before they return! Can you get out?
